mangodb stores the data in a format known as BSON

structure - 

    {
        field_1: field_1 value, 
        field_2: field_2 value,
        field_3: field_3 value,
        ....
        field_n: field_n value
    }


datatypes - 
    integer - 32
    string - "Tharun"
    array - [1, 2, 3, "Four"]
    boolean - true or false
    Null - null
    date - new Date() or "2024-02-15"
    